@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ltmecp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.15 - tmp + 0.40) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.39)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(tmp) + (wp.sin(v1 + 0.54) / v2))
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
